-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT
    TOP 100 *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://synpasedlstore.dfs.core.windows.net/root/tpchoutput/**',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) 
WITH
(
    [day] INT ,
    [C_CUSTKEY] varchar(100),
    [Tprice] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Tdicount] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Tqty] DECIMAL(14, 2),
    [Ttax] DECIMAL(10,2),
    [Titem] INT,
    [Textprice] DECIMAL(19, 2)
) AS [result]
